item.description:
Come on out and join me in a round of disc golf. We will be tossing discs along wooded paths , into metal baskets. I am not worried how well you throw, just that we all have fun. It's great exercise too ! Bring bug spray and wear good shoes. The paths are well maintained but you will be wandering into the tree areas.

I have some loaner discs and there are more FREE loaners at the Hillside store so make sure you go there first so we can all meet.

When we are done we can go back to the store and have sandwiches or icecream.

Rain will cancel this meetup ( unless it's ending around that time)

my # 603-315-0275
